hu.matech.FindInEngine

Class Route

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.matech.FindInEngine.Route

  • public class Route
extends java.lang.Object
    This contains a series of Edge. It guaranties that the Edges are in a valid rout, if the structure of the graph hasn't been changed since the adding.

    1.0
